com.yworks.yfiles.view

Class RenderContextEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • javafx.event.Event
        • com.yworks.yfiles.view.RenderContextEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEventArgs, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class RenderContextEvent
extends Event
implements IEventArgs
    The event arguments for the com.yworks.util.IEventHandler used by PrepareRenderContextEvent.

    This event argument can be used to modify the Context during CanvasControl.exportContent(IRenderContext) and CanvasControl.updateImmediately()

    See Also:
    CanvasControl#addPrepareRenderContextListener(com.yworks.util.IEventHandler), Serialized Form
